iptables -I OUTPUT -p tcp --dport 4040  -j ACCEPT; iptables -I INPUT -p tcp --dport 4040  -j ACCEPT
iptables -I OUTPUT -p tcp --dport 80    -j ACCEPT; iptables -I INPUT -p tcp --dport 80    -j ACCEPT
add manifests to:
